specific differences.

67
00:04:49,320 --> 00:04:52,340
Another recommendation is to add structure to your prompts.

68
00:04:52,900 --> 00:04:57,820
For instance, you can add subheaders to your prompts such as references and steps.

69
00:04:58,400 --> 00:05:00,460
You can include numbering and bullet points as well.

70
00:05:00,880 --> 00:05:05,780
You can also use special characters around text that you think should be treated differently

71
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:07,220
than its surrounding text.

72
