And you can choose any special characters to do this.

75
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:21,960
A common recommendation is to use three double quotes at the start and end, or use three

76
00:05:22,420 --> 00:05:24,100
hashtags at the start and the end.

77
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:29,320
These special characters that define the start and end of some specific piece of text are

78
00:05:29,460 --> 00:05:30,420
called delimiters.

